    "Achieving success at their confluence raises a critical question: when AI alone generates the intellectual content of a successful research brief or itinerary-developing new insights, proposing novel explanations, or constructing original structures-who owns the IP?",
    "The researcher or influencer who commissioned it?",
    "The AI service provider who built the system?",
    "The AI itself?",
    "Or no one at all?"
  ]
